<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.7.9">
<l>cirīitaraṉ ceyya tāmaraik kaṇṇaṉeṉṟeṉ ṟirāppakalvāy</l>
<l>verīiyala mantu kaṇkaṇīr malkivev vuyirttuyirttu</l>
<l>marīiya tīviṉai māḷaviṉ pamvaḷara vaikalvaika</l>
<l>lirīi yuṉṉaiyeṉ ṉuḷvait taṉaiye ṉiruṭīkēcaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Establishing yourself day after day so that pleasure grew, so that the evil karma died</l>
<l>that had joined me, sighing [and] sighing hotly, tears increasing in [my] eyes, being confused, frightened</l>
<l>by night and day, saying [and] saying “o bearer of Śrī, o Kṛṣṇa with red lotus eyes”,</l>
<l>you placed yourself in my heart, my Riṣikeśa.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
